content.rendered:
Directed by Israr Ahmed.

Written by Badshah Khan. S. Sachindra. Wajid Sheikh.

Cast Nawazuddin Siddiqui(Lateef). Kader Khan(Police Commissioner). Murli Sharma(Zafar Dongri). Mukesh Tiwari(ACP Sawant) . Sudesh Berry(Lateef’s Friend). Pratima Kazmi(Malkin). Irfan Razaa Khan(Inspector Pandey). Akhilendra Mishra(Narayan Dutt Agarwal). Gaurav Sameley(Gangster (as Gaurav Samoley)).Vijay Saxena. Neena Singh(Su-naina).Indranee Talukder.Pankaj Tiwari

Language Hindi.

Producers Amina Ahmad. Amina Ahmed. Rajesh Sharma.

Production Screenshot Media & Entertainment.
